00:00:13.014 --> 00:00:14.825
Nitaanza leo

00:00:14.825 --> 00:00:16.891
kwa kuigawana shairi

00:00:16.891 --> 00:00:20.026
iliyoandikiwa na rafiki yangu mmalawi,

00:00:20.026 --> 00:00:22.162
Eileen Piri.

00:00:22.162 --> 00:00:25.506
Eileen ana miaka 13 tu,

00:00:25.506 --> 00:00:31.380
lakini tulipoangalia diwani ya ushairi tuliyoandika,

00:00:31.380 --> 00:00:34.248
Niliona shairi yake ilinivuta sana,

00:00:34.248 --> 00:00:36.245
ilitia motisha sana.

00:00:36.245 --> 00:00:38.358
Basi nitakusomeeni.

00:00:38.905 --> 00:00:42.503
Ameiita shairi yake
"Nitaolewa ninapotaka"

00:00:42.503 --> 00:00:45.359
(Kicheko)

00:00:45.359 --> 00:00:47.890
"Nitaolewa ninapotaka.

00:00:47.890 --> 00:00:52.790
Mama yangu hatonilazimisha kuolewa.

00:00:52.790 --> 00:00:55.994
Baba yangu hatonilazimisha kuolewa.

00:00:57.526 --> 00:01:00.336
Mjomba, Shangazi,

00:01:00.336 --> 00:01:02.681
Kaka au dada,

00:01:02.681 --> 00:01:04.863
Hawawezi kunilazimisha.

00:01:05.885 --> 00:01:08.254
Hakuna mtu duniani

00:01:08.254 --> 00:01:11.550
awezaye kunilazimisha kuolewa.

00:01:11.550 --> 00:01:14.499
Nitaolewa ninapotaka.

00:01:14.499 --> 00:01:17.077
Hata ukinipiga,

00:01:17.077 --> 00:01:19.747
hata ukinifukuza

00:01:19.747 --> 00:01:22.928
hata ukinifanya vibaya,

00:01:22.928 --> 00:01:26.364
Nitaolewa ninapotaka.

00:01:26.364 --> 00:01:29.267
Nitaolewa ninapotaka,

00:01:29.267 --> 00:01:33.005
lakini sio kabla sijapata elimu nzuri

00:01:33.005 --> 00:01:37.323
na sio kabla sijakua mtu mzima

00:01:37.323 --> 00:01:39.810
Nitaolewa ninapotaka."

00:01:40.831 --> 00:01:43.827
Shairi inaonekana isiyo ya kawaida

00:01:43.827 --> 00:01:47.356
kuandikwa na msichana wa miaka 13,

00:01:47.356 --> 00:01:52.139
lakini tunapotoka mimi na Eileen,

00:01:52.139 --> 00:01:55.900
shairi hiyo, niliyoikusomeeni,

00:01:55.900 --> 00:01:59.616
ni sauti ya shujaa.

00:01:59.616 --> 00:02:02.541
Ninatoka Malawi.

00:02:03.191 --> 00:02:07.115
Malawi ni nchi ya maskini,

00:02:07.115 --> 00:02:09.994
maskini sana,

00:02:09.994 --> 00:02:14.522
ambapo usawa wa kijinsi sio hakika.

00:02:14.522 --> 00:02:16.844
Kukua katika nchi ile,

00:02:16.844 --> 00:02:20.095
Sikuweza kujichagulia katika maisha.

00:02:20.095 --> 00:02:22.393
Sikuweza hata kuzichungua

00:02:22.393 --> 00:02:25.389
nafasi za kibinafsi katika maisha yangu.

00:02:25.389 --> 00:02:27.919
Nitakuambieni hadithi

00:02:27.919 --> 00:02:30.381
ya wasichana wawili tofauti,

00:02:30.381 --> 00:02:34.026
wasichana wawili warembo.

00:02:34.026 --> 00:02:36.580
Hawa wasichana walikua

00:02:36.580 --> 00:02:38.693
chini ya paa moja.

00:02:38.693 --> 00:02:41.410
Walikula chakula sawa sawa.

00:02:41.410 --> 00:02:44.173
Wakati wengine, wangezigawana nguo,

00:02:44.173 --> 00:02:46.982
na hata viatu.

00:02:46.982 --> 00:02:51.649
Lakini maisha zao ziliishia tofauti,

00:02:51.649 --> 00:02:53.646
kwa njia mbili tofauti.

00:02:55.039 --> 00:02:58.754
Yule msichana mwengine ni dada yangu mdogo.

00:02:58.754 --> 00:03:03.677
Dada yangu alikuwa na miaka 11

00:03:03.677 --> 00:03:06.329
alipopata mimba.

00:03:08.029 --> 00:03:11.742
Ni jambo la kuumiza.

00:03:13.352 --> 00:03:16.633
Si kama ilimwumiza pekee, lakini mimi pia.

00:03:16.633 --> 00:03:20.232
Nilikuwa na wakati wa tafrani pia.

00:03:20.232 --> 00:03:23.947
Kwa sasa katika utamaduni wangu,

00:03:23.947 --> 00:03:26.942
ukifika ubalehe,

00:03:26.942 --> 00:03:30.820
inabidi uende makambi ya kuanzisha.

00:03:30.820 --> 00:03:33.118
Katika makambi haya,

00:03:33.118 --> 00:03:36.973
unafundishwa vipi umfurahishe mwanamume kwa kijinsia.

00:03:36.973 --> 00:03:38.761
Kuna siku maalum,

00:03:38.761 --> 00:03:41.965
wanayoiita "Siku maalum sana"

00:03:41.965 --> 00:03:44.519
ambapo mwanamume anaajiriwa na jamii

00:03:44.519 --> 00:03:47.143
anakuja kambini

00:03:47.143 --> 00:03:49.572
na anafanya mapenzi na watoto wadogo.

00:03:51.252 --> 00:03:53.766
Wazeni kiwewe wasichana hawa

00:03:53.766 --> 00:03:56.516
wanachokisikia kila siku.

00:03:58.766 --> 00:04:01.925
Wasichana wengi wanapata mimba.

00:04:01.925 --> 00:04:04.542
Na hata wanashikwa na ukimwi

00:04:04.542 --> 00:04:06.882
na magonjwa mengine ya zinaa.

00:04:07.692 --> 00:04:12.603
Kwa dadangu mdogo,
alipata mimba.

00:04:12.603 --> 00:04:16.666
Leo, ana miaka 16

00:04:16.666 --> 00:04:19.662
na ana watoto watatu.

00:04:19.662 --> 00:04:23.307
Ndoa yake ya kwanza haijaishi,

00:04:23.307 --> 00:04:26.604
wala ndoa yake ya pili.

00:04:26.604 --> 00:04:30.781
Kwa upande wengine, kuna msichana huyo.

00:04:31.341 --> 00:04:33.314
Anashangaza.

00:04:33.314 --> 00:04:35.218
(Kicheko)

00:04:35.218 --> 00:04:38.163
(Makofi)

00:04:39.723 --> 00:04:42.138
Nasema anashangaza kwa sababu ni kweli.

00:04:42.138 --> 00:04:45.203
Ni zaidi ya mzuri.

00:04:45.203 --> 00:04:48.964
Msichana yule ni mimi. (Kicheko)

00:04:48.964 --> 00:04:51.982
Nilipokuwa na miaka 13,

00:04:51.982 --> 00:04:55.396
Niliambiwa, umekua mzima,

00:04:55.396 --> 00:04:58.228
sasa umebalehe,

00:04:58.228 --> 00:05:01.595
inadhaniwa uende kambi la kuanzisha.

00:05:01.595 --> 00:05:04.567
Nilisema, "Nini?

00:05:04.567 --> 00:05:08.549
Siendi kwa yale makambi ya kuanzisha."

00:05:10.349 --> 00:05:13.112
Unajua nini mwanamke yule aliniambia?

00:05:13.112 --> 00:05:16.734
"Wewe ni mpumbavu. Mkaidi.

00:05:16.734 --> 00:05:24.001
Huziheshimu desturi za jamii yetu, za jumuia yetu."

00:05:24.001 --> 00:05:27.809
Nilikataa kwa sababu nilijua wapi nilipokwenda.

00:05:27.809 --> 00:05:30.433
Nilijua nilivyotaka katika maisha yangu.

00:05:31.773 --> 00:05:34.738
Nilikuwa na matumaini mengi nilipokuwa mtoto.

00:05:36.238 --> 00:05:39.883
Nilitaka kupata elimu nzuri

00:05:39.883 --> 00:05:42.363
Kutafuta kazi nzuri wakati wa badae.

00:05:42.363 --> 00:05:44.122
Nilikuwa najifikiria kama mwanasheria,

00:05:44.122 --> 00:05:46.832
kukaa katika kiti kile kikubwa.

00:05:46.832 --> 00:05:49.138
Yale yalikuwa mawazo

00:05:49.138 --> 00:05:52.468
yaliokuwa katika akili yangu kila siku.

00:05:52.468 --> 00:05:54.302
Na nilijua kwamba siku moja

00:05:54.302 --> 00:05:58.876
Ningesaidia kupa kitu,
kitu kidogo kwa jumuia yangu.

00:05:58.876 --> 00:06:01.407
Lakini kila siku baada ya kukataa,

00:06:01.407 --> 00:06:03.427
wanawake wangeniambia,

00:06:03.427 --> 00:06:06.817
"Jitazama, umekua mtu mzima.
Dadako mdogo amepata mtoto.

00:06:06.817 --> 00:06:08.303
Vipi wewe?"

00:06:08.303 --> 00:06:13.017
Ile ilikuwa muziki
niliyoisikia kila siku,

00:06:13.017 --> 00:06:16.894
na ile ni muziki
wasichana wanayoisikia kila siku

00:06:16.894 --> 00:06:21.043
wasipolifanya jambo
ambalo jumuia inawatakia wafanye.

00:06:23.524 --> 00:06:27.448
Nilipozilinganisha hadithi hizo mbili
kati ya mimi na dadangu,

00:06:27.448 --> 00:06:32.185
Nilisema, "Mbona nisiweze kufanya kitu?"

00:06:32.185 --> 00:06:37.246
Kwa nini nisiweze kubadilisha jambo
lililotokea kwa muda mrefu

00:06:37.246 --> 00:06:39.661
katika jamii yetu?"

00:06:39.661 --> 00:06:42.169
Wakati ule niliwaita wasichana wengine

00:06:42.169 --> 00:06:44.723
kama dadangu, ambao wamepata watoto,

00:06:44.723 --> 00:06:48.187
waliokwenda darasani lakini
wamesahau kusoma na kuandika.

00:06:48.187 --> 00:06:50.297
Nilisema "Njoo, tukumbushane

00:06:50.297 --> 00:06:52.432
je kusoma na kuandika tena,

00:06:52.432 --> 00:06:56.240
kuikamata kalamu vipi,
kusomaje, kuzuia kitabu."

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:59.885
Ilikuwa wakati nzuri sana nao.

00:06:59.885 --> 00:07:04.157
Sio kwamba nilifundishwa kidogo kuhusu wale,

00:07:04.157 --> 00:07:07.594
lakini pia waliweza kuniambia 
hadithi zao za kibinafsi,

00:07:07.594 --> 00:07:09.405
waliyokabiliana kila siku

00:07:09.405 --> 00:07:12.075
kama mama wadogo.

00:07:12.075 --> 00:07:14.072
Wakati ule nilidhani,

00:07:14.072 --> 00:07:17.996
"Kwa nini tusiweze kuangalia mambo hayo
yanayotuathiri

00:07:17.996 --> 00:07:21.873
na kuyaonesha na kuwaambia mama zao,
viongozi wetu wa jadi,

00:07:21.873 --> 00:07:23.870
kwamba mambo hayo ni maovu?"

00:07:23.870 --> 00:07:25.937
Ilikuwa jambo la hofu,

00:07:25.937 --> 00:07:27.910
kwa sababu viongozi hawa wa jadi,

00:07:27.910 --> 00:07:30.114
wameshayazoea mambo

00:07:30.114 --> 00:07:32.554
yaliyokuwepo kwa muda mrefu.

00:07:32.554 --> 00:07:34.481
Ni jambo ambalo ni ngumu kubadilisha,

00:07:34.481 --> 00:07:37.105
lakini nzuri kujitahidi.

00:07:37.105 --> 00:07:39.357
Kwa hiyo tulijitahidi.

00:07:39.357 --> 00:07:41.865
Ilikuwa ngumu sana, lakini tulivumulia.

00:07:42.245 --> 00:07:45.109
Na mimi nipo kwa kusema kwamba katika jumuia yangu,

00:07:45.109 --> 00:07:47.669
ilikuwa jumuia ya kwanza baada ya wasichana

00:07:47.669 --> 00:07:51.036
walijitahidi sana kumthibitishia kiongozi wa jadi wetu,

00:07:51.036 --> 00:07:55.425
na kiongozi wetu alitutetea
na akasema hakuna msichana 
alazimishwaye kuolewa

00:07:55.425 --> 00:07:57.654
kabla hajafika miaka 18.

00:07:57.654 --> 00:08:01.507
(Makofi)

00:08:05.502 --> 00:08:07.243
Katika jumuia yangu

00:08:07.243 --> 00:08:09.890
Ilikuwa mara ya kwanza kwa jumuia,

00:08:09.890 --> 00:08:12.351
ilibidi watazame sheria ndogo,

00:08:12.351 --> 00:08:15.858
ya kwanza iliyowalinda wasichana

00:08:15.858 --> 00:08:18.052
katika jumuia yetu.

00:08:18.052 --> 00:08:19.840
Hatukumaliza na hivyo.

00:08:19.840 --> 00:08:22.789
Tuliendelea.

00:08:22.789 --> 00:08:26.643
Tulikusudia kuwapigania wasichana
sio katika jamii yangu tu

00:08:26.643 --> 00:08:29.429
lakini kwenye jamii nyingine.

00:08:29.429 --> 00:08:33.562
Wakati muswada wa ndoa za watoto
iliwasilishwa mwezi wa pili

00:08:33.562 --> 00:08:37.208
tulikuwepo kwenye mahakama ya bunge.

00:08:37.208 --> 00:08:41.294
Kila siku, wakati wabunge 
walipoingia,

00:08:41.294 --> 00:08:44.383
tulikuwa tukiwaambia,
"Tafadhali uitegemee muswada hii?"

00:08:44.383 --> 00:08:49.142
Na hatuna
teknolojia nyingi kama huku,

00:08:49.142 --> 00:08:51.139
lakini tunazo simu zetu ndogo.

00:08:51.139 --> 00:08:56.169
Kwa hiyo tulisema, "Mbona tusiweze kupata 
namba zao na kuwatumia text?"

00:08:56.178 --> 00:08:59.428
Kwa hiyo tulifanya hivyo. 
Na ilikuwa jambo zuri

00:08:59.428 --> 00:09:01.448
(Makofi)

00:09:01.448 --> 00:09:04.421
Kwa hiyo muswada ilipokubalika,
tuliwajibia na text,

00:09:04.421 --> 00:09:06.849
"Asante kwa kutegemea muswada."

00:09:06.849 --> 00:09:07.919
(Kicheko)

00:09:07.919 --> 00:09:11.264
Na muswada iliposajilika
na Rais,

00:09:11.264 --> 00:09:14.630
kwa kuifanya kuwa sheria, ilikuwa ziada.

00:09:14.630 --> 00:09:20.482
Sasa, katika Malawi, miaka 18 ni umri wa
kisheria kuolewa, kutoka 15 hadi 18.

00:09:20.482 --> 00:09:24.127
(Makofi)

00:09:26.495 --> 00:09:30.071
Ni jambo zuri kulijua
kwamba muswada imakubalika,

00:09:30.071 --> 00:09:33.113
lakini nikuambieni:

00:09:33.113 --> 00:09:37.501
Kuna nchi ambako miaka 18
ni umri wa kisheria kuolewa,

00:09:37.501 --> 00:09:41.773
lakini sio tunasikia kilio
za wanawake na wasichana kila siku?

00:09:41.773 --> 00:09:47.416
Kila siku, maisha ya wasichana
yanashuka thamani.

00:09:47.416 --> 00:09:53.870
Ni wakati muhimu kwa viongozi waiheshimu ahadi yao.

00:09:53.870 --> 00:09:56.239
Kwa kuiheshimu ahadi hiyo,

00:09:56.239 --> 00:10:01.951
inamaanisha kuyaweka maswala ya wasichana
moyoni kila mara.

00:10:01.951 --> 00:10:05.712
Tusitiishiwe kama duni,

00:10:05.712 --> 00:10:09.950
lakini wajue kwamba wanawake,
kama sisi chumbani humu,

00:10:09.950 --> 00:10:13.000
sisi sio wanawake tu,
sisi sio wasichana tu,

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:14.980
sisi ni wa ajabu.

00:10:14.980 --> 00:10:16.893
Tunaweza kufanya zaidi.

00:10:16.893 --> 00:10:19.888
Na kitu chengine kwa Malawi,

00:10:19.888 --> 00:10:22.790
na si kwa Malawi pekee lakini nchi nyingine pia:

00:10:22.790 --> 00:10:26.575
Sheria zinazowepo,

00:10:26.575 --> 00:10:32.426
mnajua sheria sio sheria 
mpaka inatekeleza?

00:10:32.426 --> 00:10:35.839
Sheria iliyokubalika juzi

00:10:35.839 --> 00:10:38.463
na sheria ambazo katika nchi nyingine
zimekuwepo,

00:10:38.463 --> 00:10:42.387
zinahitajika kutangazwa
kwa njia za kienyeji,

00:10:42.387 --> 00:10:44.570
katika jamii,

00:10:44.570 --> 00:10:49.956
ambako maswala ya wasichana yako wazi.

00:10:49.956 --> 00:10:54.716
Wasichana wanakabiliana na maswala,
maswala magumu, katika jamii zao kila siku.

00:10:55.274 --> 00:11:00.359
Kwa hiyo ikiwa wajue kwamba
kuna sheria ziwalindazo,

00:11:00.359 --> 00:11:03.145
wataweza kusimama
na kujilinda

00:11:03.145 --> 00:11:06.816
kwa sababu watajua kwamba
kuna sheria ziwalindazo.

00:11:09.254 --> 00:11:13.363
Na kitu chengine nisemacho ni kwamba

00:11:13.363 --> 00:11:17.961
sauti za wasichana na wanawake

00:11:17.961 --> 00:11:20.724
ni nzuri sana, na zipo,

00:11:20.724 --> 00:11:23.905
lakini hatuwezi kufanya peke yetu.

00:11:23.905 --> 00:11:26.575
watetezi wa kiume, washirikiana,

00:11:26.575 --> 00:11:28.525
wajihusishe na tufanye kazi pamoja.

00:11:28.525 --> 00:11:31.103
ni kazi ya umoja.

00:11:31.103 --> 00:11:33.843
Tunavyohitaji ni vile vihitajikavyo 
na wasichana wa sehemu zote:

00:11:33.843 --> 00:11:39.601
elimu nzuri, na juu ya yote,
ni kutoolewa wakiwa na miaka 11.

00:11:42.085 --> 00:11:44.953
Na zaidi ya hayo,

00:11:44.953 --> 00:11:48.018
Najua kwamba pamoja,

00:11:48.018 --> 00:11:51.966
tunaweza kubadilisha mifumo ya kisheria,

00:11:51.966 --> 00:11:55.135
kiutamaduni na kisiasa

00:11:55.135 --> 00:11:59.906
inayozikanusha haki za wasichana.

00:11:59.906 --> 00:12:04.964
Nasimama hapa leo

00:12:04.964 --> 00:12:12.004
na kutangaza kwamba tunaweza
kuisha ndoa za watoto katika kizazi kimoja.

00:12:12.677 --> 00:12:14.860
Sasa ni wakati

00:12:14.860 --> 00:12:19.294
ambapo msichana na msichana,
na millioni za wasichana duniani,

00:12:19.294 --> 00:12:21.895
wataweza kusema,

00:12:21.895 --> 00:12:25.099
"Nitolewa ninapotaka."

00:12:25.099 --> 00:12:28.144
(Makofi)

00:12:35.284 --> 00:12:37.219
Asante. (Makofi)

